DASHBOARD NAVIGATION FLOW:

Dashboard Quick Actions
        ↓
[Add New Pet] → data-section="profiles"
        ↓
Profiles Section (Pet List)
        ↓
[+ Add New Pet] → data-action="showAddForm"
        ↓  
Pet Creation Form
        ↓
[Submit] → Saves pet → Returns to Profiles Section
        ↓
[Set as Active] → data-action="setCurrentPet" 
        ↓
Returns to Dashboard (with pet summary)

Navigation Buttons:
- [Back to Dashboard] (Profiles Section) → Returns to main dashboard
- [Cancel] (Pet Form) → Returns to profiles section

- Nutrition section.

User Opens Nutrition Section
         ↓
[Check if Active Pet Selected]
         ↓
     [No Pet] → Show "Select Pet First" Message
         ↓
     [Has Pet] → Display Nutrition Dashboard
         ↓
         ├─ Calorie Calculator
         │     ↓
         │  [User Adjusts Activity Level/Weight Goal]
